OL,3,CAngela Rayner resigns from government,
OL,4,CITV News understands
OL,6,FAngela Rayner has resigned as deputy
OL,7,Fprime minister and housing minister
OL,8,Ffollowing an investigation into her
OL,9,Ftax affairs by an independent ethics
OL,10,Fadvisor, ITV News understands.
OL,12,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Freceived the report by Sir Laurie
OL,14,FMagnus on Wednesday morning.
OL,16,FRayner was facing mounting pressure
OL,17,Fafter she admitted on Wednesday she
OL,18,Fhad underpaid stamp duty on an
OL,19,F#800,000 flat in Hove, which is
OL,20,Fconsidered to be her second home.
