OL,3,CAngela Rayner resigns from government,
OL,4,CITV News understands
OL,6,FShe initially said she had been
OL,7,Fadvised she was not liable for the
OL,8,Fsecond property surcharge because she
OL,9,Fhad sold her stake in her family home
OL,10,Fin Ashton-under-Lyne to a trust
OL,11,Festablished in 2020 to benefit her
OL,12,Fdisabled son.
OL,14,FBut she conceded she had made a
OL,15,F"mistake" after fresh legal advice
OL,16,Ffrom a "leading tax counsel" later
OL,17,Frevealed that she was liable.
