OL,3,CAngela Rayner resigns from government,
OL,4,CITV News understands
OL,6,FIn the statement on Wednesday, Rayner
OL,7,Fadmitted: "I acknowledge that due to
OL,8,Fmy reliance on advice from lawyers
OL,9,Fwhich did not properly take account of
OL,10,Fthese provisions, I did not pay the
OL,11,Fappropriate stamp duty at the time of
OL,12,Fthe purchase.
OL,14,F"I am working with expert lawyers and
OL,15,Fwith HMRC to resolve the matter and
OL,16,Fpay what is due."
OL,18,FBefore then, she had insisted for
OL,19,Fweeks that she had paid the correct
OL,20,Famount of tax.
