OL,3,CAngela Rayner resigns from government,
OL,4,CITV News understands
OL,6,FSources close to Rayner also said a
OL,7,Fconveyancer and two experts in trust
OL,8,Flaw had all suggested the amount of
OL,9,Fstamp duty she paid on the East Sussex
OL,10,Fproperty was correct and she acted on
OL,11,Fthe advice she was given at the time.
OL,13,FBut the conveyancing firm, Verrico and
OL,14,FAssociates, on Thursday said its
OL,15,Flawyers "never" gave Rayner tax advice
OL,16,Fand were being made "scapegoats".
