OL,3,CAngela Rayner resigns from government,
OL,4,CITV News understands
OL,6,FIn a statement, managing director
OL,7,FJoanna Verrico said: "We're not
OL,8,Fqualified to give advice on trust and
OL,9,Ftax matters and we advise clients to
OL,10,Fseek expert advice on these."
OL,12,FThe founder of the small high street
OL,13,Ffirm, based in Herne Bay, Kent, said
OL,14,Fit completed her stamp duty return
OL,15,F"based on the figures and the
OL,16,Finformation provided by Rayner".
OL,18,FRayner first became an MP in 2015 and
OL,19,Fmade history by becoming the first
OL,20,Fwoman to hold the Ashton-under-Lyne
OL,21,Fconstituency.
